@startuml Trust Centre — User Level
title Trust Centre (Public Profile & Contact)

actor "Visitor" as visitor
actor "Org Admin" as admin
participant "Trust Centre Page" as mp
participant "Org Profile" as profile
participant "Trust Centre Settings" as settings
participant "Contact Form" as contact

== Browsing the Trust Centre ==

visitor -> mp : Visits /trust-centre\n(public, no login required)
visitor -> mp : Sees list of organisations\nwith public profiles
visitor -> mp : Can search and filter

== Viewing an Organisation ==

visitor -> mp : Clicks on an org card
mp -> profile : Opens /trust-centre/:orgId
visitor -> profile : Sees organisation details:\n- Description\n- Products listed\n- Compliance summary\n- Contact option

== Contacting an Organisation ==

visitor -> profile : Clicks "Contact"
profile -> contact : Contact form opens
visitor -> contact : Enters name, email, message
visitor -> contact : Clicks "Send"
contact -> contact : Confirmation shown:\n"Message sent"
note right of contact : Organisation receives\na notification about\nthe new contact.

== Managing Trust Centre Profile ==

admin -> settings : Navigates to\n/trust-centre/settings
admin -> settings : Edits organisation\ndescription and details
admin -> settings : Toggles trust-centre\nvisibility on/off
admin -> settings : Clicks "Save"
settings -> settings : Profile updated
note right of settings : Changes reflect\nimmediately on the\npublic trust-centre page.

@enduml
